  "importedComments": [
    {
      "id": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg",
      "text": "このころは黒ひげがちょっと変わった良い奴なイメージだったなぁ…",
      "author": "@ilovesupura-owl",
      "likeCount": 8877,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T02:26:34Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg.AKSvgcVLKR7AKTfWlYKuSu",
      "text": "海賊らしくていいやん。俺は麦わらのほうがイメージ良くないよ",
      "author": "@dddd4c",
      "likeCount": 616,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T09:24:31Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "text": "ルフィは打撃効かないからいいけど\n巻き込まれたゾロはしっかりダメージ負わされてんのおもろい",
      "author": "@れとろげーまー",
      "likeCount": 4825,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T13:23:40Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg.AKU5tQiTiSPAKVc3OewvDf",
      "text": "ベラミーさん、既に武装色を使っていた疑惑",
      "author": "@mama_mama_mama_mama_mama",
      "likeCount": 137,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-13T03:32:46Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg.AKU5tQiTiSPAKWFgqxOBP1",
      "text": "なにもな゛かった...",
      "author": "@mgpoc",
      "likeCount": 23,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-13T09:27:49Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "text": "黒ひげが「今の戦いはそいつらの勝ちだぜ」って言ってくれるのいいな",
      "author": "@ホロライブとワンピースが好きな男",
      "likeCount": 3486,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-20T01:09:47Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg.AKmOGEokjgyAUb9rIKSE_j",
      "text": "黒ひげは理解はするけど自分は普通に悪党やるもんな",
      "author": "@たつ-v4h9i",
      "likeCount": 16,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2026-03-21T05:46:12Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg.AKmOGEokjgyAVUPgmv9fsX",
      "text": "@朝マック-u6d海賊らしくて草",
      "author": "@ミケランジェロ-1",
      "likeCount": 8,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2026-04-12T02:02:03Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "text": "この時期のワンピは間違いなく名作だった",
      "author": "@チャイカツ",
      "likeCount": 1142,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-10-25T13:17:07Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg.AOhSbF-_4wIAQiFsNJ-OHn",
      "text": "今では神が出てきて、王がぼこぼこにされて、キャラの実力に差があって、昔死んだ奴はインフレに取り残されて雑魚みたいになってるもんな、それでもまぁ面白いから好きだけど",
      "author": "@user-melon-metamo-tapioka",
      "likeCount": 44,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-14T13:47:53Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg.AOhSbF-_4wIAQpaQAw0TtJ",
      "text": "アラバスタ←名作\n空島←秀作\nエニエスロビー←神",
      "author": "@jyodagiri",
      "likeCount": 137,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-17T10:10:49Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg.AOhSbF-_4wIARLpPSMfvmm",
      "text": "黒ひげいいこと言うじゃん",
      "author": "@サワシン-j2k",
      "likeCount": 5,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-30T07:56:44Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgyvRdRXk9Qn6JibjBt4AaABAg",
      "text": "ベラミーは敵としてめっちゃ魅力あったわ。\n噛ませとしてめっちゃよく描けてて秀逸なキャラだった。",
      "author": "@ハニ-j1b",
      "likeCount": 908,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T20:49:58Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgyvRdRXk9Qn6JibjBt4AaABAg.AKUtyBmQJVHAQa7KoxJ2oo",
      "text": "ドフラミンゴの時はマジで泣いた…",
      "author": "@swallow_children",
      "likeCount": 0,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgyvRdRXk9Qn6JibjBt4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-11T09:59:20Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwX9dAWrYk7Rba5bbN4AaABAg",
      "text": "この後ルフィがワンパンしてるの見てかなりスカッとした印象ある。",
      "author": "@ゆとり世代代表",
      "likeCount": 369,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T07:51:21Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwX9dAWrYk7Rba5bbN4AaABAg.AKTVrNQmDHsAKgBc2WIVs9",
      "text": "ゴムゴムすら使ってない",
      "author": "@ちくしゃ-m5h",
      "likeCount": 4,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwX9dAWrYk7Rba5bbN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-17T15:23:52Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwX9dAWrYk7Rba5bbN4AaABAg.AKTVrNQmDHsAKiWUXMRxGz",
      "text": "パンチの打ち方を知ってるかって？",
      "author": "@時の旅人-o2h",
      "likeCount": 9,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwX9dAWrYk7Rba5bbN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-18T13:04:41Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgyduwxGBJ4ZeeCksW54AaABAg",
      "text": "このシーンのせいで黒髭嫌いになれない、、",
      "author": "@nobuo1972",
      "likeCount": 192,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T04:10:38Z"
    },
    {
